<p>John and Dave discuss tracking Mail.app&rsquo;s rule processing, dealing with small web page fonts, managing SMTP server ports, and backing up IMAP mail. Additionally, they talk through using and migrating to the new MobileMe CalDAV calendar and why you should &mdash; or shouldn&rsquo;t &mdash; bother to do it. A great show today &mdash; don&rsquo;t miss it!</p>
